a al aprendizaje automático. ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.oreilly.com\/library\/view\/probability-and-statistics\/9780137566273\/#:~:text=,theory%20and%20statistical%20modeling","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"“Data Science from Scratch”","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" por Joel Grus. Este libro empieza desde cero y construye tu comprensión de los fundamentos de la ciencia de datos, usando Python. ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.oreilly.com\/library\/view\/data-science-from\/9781492041122\/","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MIT, EdX y YouTube:"}]}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“Mathematics for Machine Learning”: Un curso que enseña el kit de herramientas matemáticas fundamentales para el aprendizaje automático, incluyendo cálculo, álgebra lineal, estadísticas y probabilidad. Enlace."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“Linear Algebra - Foundations to Frontiers” (LAFF): Curso del MIT que profundiza en álgebra lineal y su relación con vectores y matrices. https:\/\/www.edx.org\/learn\/linear-algebra\/the-university-of-texas-at-austin-linear-algebra-foundations-to-frontiers"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“Introduction to Probability - The Science of Uncertainty”: Curso del MIT que ofrece una base sólida en teoría de probabilidades y sus aplicaciones. "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ocw.mit.edu\/courses\/6-041sc-probabilistic-systems-analysis-and-applied-probability-fall-2013\/"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"https:\/\/ocw.mit.edu\/favicon.ico","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineConten